question_id: Daftar judul film beserta nama bahasa untuk semua film berdurasi lebih dari 184 menit.
sql_query:
SELECT
  f.title AS judul_film,
  l.name AS nama_bahasa
FROM film AS f
JOIN language AS l
  ON f.language_id = l.language_id
WHERE
  f.length > 184
raw_response:
```sql
SELECT
  f.title AS judul_film,
  l.name AS nama_bahasa
```
